embeds.description: -# Here are all the available music commands you can use:

fields.value: Toggles the 24/7 mode. This makes the bot doesn't leave the voice channel until you stop it.

fields.name: /autoplay
fields.value: Toggles autoplay for the current guild.

fields.name: /nowplaying
fields.value: Shows what is song that the bot is currently playing.

fields.name: /play
fields.value: Add a song to queue and plays it.

fields.name: /previous
fields.value: Plays the previous song in the queue.

fields.name: /queue
fields.value: Display the queue of the current tracks in the playlist.

fields.name: /stop
fields.value: Stop the current song and clears the entire music queue.

embeds.title: Music Commands
